5:49:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0afd6b0d2766602ae4a1d208734216b84afbf23","tid":1723082,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb80d8cdb8b493938266b7109c18a507fce59d0","tid":1723082,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546a825489063a6a23389dc33ae3810bbf27fad9","tid":1723082,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:20:16.000Z","msg":"獨立關稅區（separate customs territory，單獨關稅區、單獨關境、個別關稅領域）為關稅暨貿易總協定(GATT)及其繼承者世界貿易組織(WTO)相關術語，為對其締約方（即成員）的總稱，因締約方屬政府組織，以主權國家政府為主，包括非主權的政治實體政府。<br />\n<br />\n「獨立關稅區」原為GATT誕生之初，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為尚未獲得完全獨立的殖民地政府當局而設置。</span></span>GATT成立之初以「獨立關稅區」的非主權政治實體達30餘個。1960年代後，隨着殖民地獨立，作為「獨立關稅區」的非主權政治實體漸漸減少。目前在WTO存在四個單獨關稅區，即歐盟、台澎金馬、香港及澳門。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆街美國佬嚴重干涉香港內政</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0982ba2c2935a7a36eb8c8d0ea3416cc670c3a5b","tid":1723082,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c504bb85a0102c68116af05e08f6ed4c8e72bfa","tid":1723082,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5051ddb00cadb77dbbaeee3c9ccaca535a1dec52","tid":1723082,"uid":305982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷<br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士、中午中環射催淚彈、警察街上捉返學嘅女學生、以及警察話上堂等於非法集結，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！"},{"pid":"3690b8202538385ef27b724c11d8c0ce2a24a5d7","tid":1723082,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7d5aa357f706d5dc9ec136d2a9e0e960442d8c","tid":1723082,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"我地香港自古以來全靠祖國，97金融風暴，03自由行，洗撚你美國佬獨立關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ed7ff12b0b094084b2fa67be6e6a35729cd4b9","tid":1723082,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}